# DiffDrone Single Agent Configuration
# DiffDrone 单智能体训练配置
#
# This configuration is optimized for single-agent quadrotor flight training.
# Use this configuration when training a single quadrotor to navigate
# through obstacles to reach a target position.
#
# 该配置针对单智能体四轴飞行器飞行训练进行了优化。
# 在训练单个四轴飞行器穿越障碍物到达目标位置时使用此配置。

# Enable single-agent mode / 启用单智能体模式
# When enabled, only 1 quadrotor is simulated per batch
# 启用时，每批只模拟1个四轴飞行器
--single

# Speed multiplier for target velocity / 目标速度的乘数
# Range of target speeds: [0.75, 3.25] m/s (with speed_mtp=4)
# 目标速度范围：[0.75, 3.25] m/s（当speed_mtp=4时）
# Higher values encourage faster flight but may reduce stability
# 较高值鼓励更快飞行，但可能降低稳定性
--speed_mtp 4

# Acceleration smoothing loss weight / 加速度平滑损失权重
# Loss term: sum(act^2) / batch_size
# Encourages smaller accelerations to protect hardware and improve comfort
# 鼓励较小的加速度以保护硬件并提高舒适性
# Typical range: 0.005 - 0.05
--coef_d_acc 0.01

# Jerk smoothing loss weight / Jerk平滑损失权重
# Loss term: sum((act(t+1) - act(t))^2) / batch_size
# Penalizes rapid changes in acceleration for smoother flight
# 惩罚加速度的快速变化以实现更平滑的飞行
# Typical range: 0.0005 - 0.005
--coef_d_jerk 0.001

# Add ground obstacles / 添加地面障碍物
# When enabled, adds hemispherical obstacles on the ground
# that require the quadrotor to fly higher
# 启用时，在地面添加半球形障碍物，要求四轴飞行器飞得更高
# Improves vertical flight capability and altitude control
# 改善垂直飞行能力和高度控制
--ground_voxels

# Enable random rotation of the environment / 启用环境随机旋转
# Randomly rotates the entire scene around the z-axis (yaw)
# 随机地围绕z轴（偏航）旋转整个场景
# Helps the model learn rotation-invariant policies
# 帮助模型学习旋转不变策略
--random_rotation

# Enable yaw drift disturbance / 启用偏航漂移扰动
# Adds random yaw angle drift over time, simulating gyroscope bias
# 随时间添加随机偏航角漂移，模拟陀螺仪偏置
# Improves robustness to sensor bias
# 提高对传感器偏置的鲁棒性
--yaw_drift

# Collision loss weight / 碰撞损失权重
# Loss term: softplus(-32 * distance) * approaching_velocity
# Exponential penalty when very close to obstacles
# 非常接近障碍物时的指数惩罚
# Higher values make collision avoidance more aggressive
# 较高值使避障更激进
# Typical range: 5.0 - 10.0 for obstacle-rich environments
--coef_collide 7.5

# Obstacle avoidance loss weight / 避障损失权重
# Loss term: approaching_velocity * max(0, 1 - distance)^2
# Quadratic penalty when approaching obstacles
# 接近障碍物时的二次惩罚
# Higher values encourage staying further from obstacles
# 较高值鼓励保持离障碍物更远
--coef_obj_avoidance 3.0

# Camera pitch angle in degrees / 相机俯仰角（度）
# Angle below horizontal, looking slightly downward
# 水平以下的角度，略微向下看
# Typical range: 10 - 30 degrees
# 10: Slight downward pitch / 轻微向下俯仰
# 20: Moderate downward pitch / 中等向下俯仰
# 30: Steep downward pitch / 陡峭向下俯仰
--cam_angle 20

# Horizontal field of view / 水平视场角
# Half-tangent of horizontal FOV angle
# 水平视场角的一半正切
# Larger values give wider field of view (see more obstacles)
# 较大值提供更宽的视野（看到更多障碍物）
# Typical range: 0.53 (standard) - 0.82 (wide)
--fov_x_half_tan 0.82
